{"tid":2223060,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大開宗教、哲學及倫理文學士  享受緊密師生關係","createTime":"2020-09-29T13:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T13:20:35.000Z","uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"40e5da496139302ff8e8b261d392e23d5e48e7bd","tid":2223060,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T13:51:27.000Z","msg":"現有之宗教研究文學士（榮譽）學位課程於2019年起更名及改革為宗教、哲學及倫理文學士（榮譽）學位課程。修讀新課程的學生將會學習到寫作、公開演講及批判思考的技巧，也會享受到緊密的師生關係。本課程融會宗教、哲學及倫理三個不同而緊密相關的學術領域，為香港乃至亞洲首創學士課程。諸如宗教、哲學及倫理的多元科際課程是近年全球其中一個發展最蓬勃的課程，著名例子包括英國的倫敦國王學院和諾丁漢大學也有提供此課程。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d169c94ed5dc26acae2a35dab7a97d4e57d0fc4e","tid":2223060,"uid":246986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T13:52:21.000Z","msg":"緊密關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a770ddfea1a71522214fc31515e406105cd754","tid":2223060,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d169c94ed5dc26acae2a35dab7a97d4e57d0fc4e","tid":2223060,"uid":246986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T13:52:21.000Z","msg":"緊密關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T13:54:34.000Z","msg":"Hello Moto"},{"pid":"665a695847dce21956f5df2faafb33f8b2b08f1e","tid":2223060,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T13:55:32.000Z","msg":"想知究竟學到啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4145ea83fcc0118de7c6f106995cb4df0711057e","tid":2223060,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T13:57:29.000Z","msg":"Intimacy<img src=\"/assets/face